name: Catch It! (To Sky)
description:
Hello...

Hi dear player. Here is demo version of my game. Please rate It. Please donate if you have extra money. It helps us make better games. Write a comment below.

Story

It's a story about Adam (your trainer) and You(You want to become a famous singer). In each level you need train an train. It's just a demo version of the game. Wait for It...

Controls(important)

Use buttons Up Arrow, Down Arrow, Right Arrow, Left Arrow on your keyboard.  Be attentive to each object. Don't worry if game is too hard for you. You need train, train and train.

Try to get as far as you can.
